{"id":89,"category_slug":"short-stories","category_name":"Short Stories","position":59,"title":"59. Which direction?","subtitle":"","level":"B1","parts":21,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/short-stories/59-which-direction.89/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/0-59-which-direction.mp3","transcript":"Which direction should I go in?\nShould I go up?\nIf I go up, I will head toward the sky.\nI can go up the stairs.\nShould I go down?\nI can go down the stairs to the basement.\nI can climb down into a hole.\nShould I go left or right?\nI am right-handed, so I know which way right is.\nShould I go backwards?\nI would be going away from the things that I am facing now if I went backwards.\nIf I went backwards from the thing that I am facing,\nI would go away from it.\nShould I go forward?\nI will just go straight ahead if I go forward.\nIf I am facing something and I go forward,\nthen I will go toward the thing that I am facing.\nMaybe I should go sideways,\nbut which side, left or right?\nIt sounds very complicated, but it is not.\nDirections are very easy to follow if you just stop and think about them.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:55:51","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Which direction should I go in?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/1.mp3","time_start":3.2,"time_end":5.4},{"position":2,"content":"Should I go up?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/2.mp3","time_start":5.4,"time_end":6.6},{"position":3,"content":"If I go up, I will head toward the sky.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/3.mp3","time_start":6.7,"time_end":9.4},{"position":4,"content":"I can go up the stairs.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/4.mp3","time_start":9.6,"time_end":11.3},{"position":5,"content":"Should I go down?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/5.mp3","time_start":11.6,"time_end":12.84},{"position":6,"content":"I can go down the stairs to the basement.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/6.mp3","time_start":13.0,"time_end":15.5},{"position":7,"content":"I can climb down into a hole.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/7.mp3","time_start":15.5,"time_end":17.6},{"position":8,"content":"Should I go left or right?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/8.mp3","time_start":18.24,"time_end":20.2},{"position":9,"content":"I am right-handed, so I know which way right is.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/9.mp3","time_start":20.26,"time_end":23.6},{"position":10,"content":"Should I go backwards?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/10.mp3","time_start":24.2,"time_end":25.7},{"position":11,"content":"I would be going away from the things that I am facing now if I went backwards.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/11.mp3","time_start":26.1,"time_end":31.0},{"position":12,"content":"If I went backwards from the thing that I am facing,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/12.mp3","time_start":31.2,"time_end":34.2},{"position":13,"content":"I would go away from it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/13.mp3","time_start":34.2,"time_end":36.0},{"position":14,"content":"Should I go forward?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/14.mp3","time_start":36.3,"time_end":37.8},{"position":15,"content":"I will just go straight ahead if I go forward.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/15.mp3","time_start":38.15,"time_end":40.8},{"position":16,"content":"If I am facing something and I go forward,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/16.mp3","time_start":41.09,"time_end":43.9},{"position":17,"content":"then I will go toward the thing that I am facing.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/17.mp3","time_start":43.9,"time_end":47.0},{"position":18,"content":"Maybe I should go sideways,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/18.mp3","time_start":47.5,"time_end":49.7},{"position":19,"content":"but which side, left or right?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/19.mp3","time_start":49.8,"time_end":52.7},{"position":20,"content":"It sounds very complicated, but it is not.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/20.mp3","time_start":53.0,"time_end":56.4},{"position":21,"content":"Directions are very easy to follow if you just stop and think about them.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/59-which-direction-2019-03-29-10-26-18/21.mp3","time_start":56.72,"time_end":61.3}]}